        "text": ", of the rebuilding of ruins. The general remark, ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "1 Chronicles 11:9",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ", \"and David increased continually in might,\" etc., opens the way for the transition to the history of David's reign which follows. As a proof of his increasing greatness, there follows in  ",
        "children": []
      }
    ]
  }
